snippet.title: Strongford Penitentiary Lost Tape 91 Teaser Trailer - Urbex "The Lost Tapes" Series
snippet.description:
Strongford Penitentiary Lost Tape 91 Has been released! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/strongford-penitentiary-lost-tape-91 The first entry in the new upcoming series "The Lost Tapes" Featuring 3 unique titles. 

Story: Strongford Penitentiary, a former residence for the criminally insane and mentally deranged, active for over 50 years the premise housed the countries most dangerous inmates. Explore the decrepit building and use your camera to unfold the gruesome past events and history. 

You've survived the "Incident Tapes" Series, now it's time to put your urban exploration skills and sanity to the ultimate test.

VHS Urbex Found Footage "The Lost Tapes" Series will contain:
 Strongford Penitentiary Lost Tape 91 - Paid
 Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 - Paid 
 Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 - Paid

Strongford Penitentiary Lost Tape 91 is a VHS Urban Exploration Found Footage horror title with emphasis on atmosphere, unpredictability, realism and a non-linear design with multiple endings and outcomes.

VHS Urbex Found Footage "Incident" Tape Series is OUT! Buy now on Itch - 4 titles:

    Grainwind Incident 77 - Free https://azagamestudio.itch.io/grainwind-incident-77
    Sanevol Incident 44 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/grainwind-incident-77
    Lakelight Elementary Incident 68 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/lakelight-elementary-incident-68
    Nihil Ignis Incident 48 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/nihil-ignis-incident-48
